                            <comment id="14428668" author="hayos" created="Fri, 4 Feb 2011 06:50:00 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;According to &lt;a href=&quot;http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MCOMPILER-70&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;http://jira.codehaus.org/browse/MCOMPILER-70&lt;/a&gt; fixed in 2.1. So the correct documentation would be:&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;The -encoding argument for the Java compiler.&lt;br/&gt;
Since 2.1: Default value is: ${project.build.sourceEncoding}.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
